				<tei-p data-origname="p"><tei-distinct type="abundance" data-origname="distinct">Many</tei-distinct><tei-distinct type="variety" data-origname="distinct">variations</tei-distinct> of <tei-objecttype data-origname="objectType">grotesques</tei-objecttype> and <tei-objecttype data-origname="objectType">compartments</tei-objecttype> made <tei-distinct type="utility" data-origname="distinct">for the use of</tei-distinct> <tei-name type="profession" data-origname="name">all those who love and use art.</tei-name> Printed by <tei-name type="printer" data-origname="name">Hieronymus Cock</tei-name> <tei-date data-origname="date">1556</tei-date>.</tei-p>
				<tei-p data-origname="p"><tei-name type="designer" data-origname="name">Cornelis Floris</tei-name> invented.</tei-p>
				<tei-p data-origname="p">First book.</tei-p>
			</tei-div>
			<tei-div facs="#f000_z055" data-origname="div">
				<tei-p data-origname="p">With grace and privilege</tei-p>
			</tei-div>
		</tei-body>
	</tei-text>
